<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.4">
<l>māṭṭātē yākilu malartalaimā ñālaniṉ</l>
<l>māṭṭāya malarpuraiyun tiruvuruva maṉamvaikka</l>
<l>māṭṭāta palacamaya matikoṭuttāy malartuḻāy</l>
<l>māṭṭēnī maṉamvaittāy māñālam varuntātē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though the great world of blooming area is unable,</l>
<l>you gave thought to many creeds that are unable</l>
<l>to put the mind on the form of Śrī who resembles a blossom that is on you.</l>
<l>You put [your] mind on the blooming Tulsi. The great world won’t suffer.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
